#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.exp.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.exp"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.exp.exp:1 of
msgid "Calculate the exponential of all elements in the input tensor."
msgstr "计算输入张量中所有元素的指数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.exp.exp of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.exp.exp:3 of
msgid "Input values."
msgstr "输入值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.exp.exp:5 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须与输入广播一致。如果未提供或为 `"
"None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（仅可作为关键字参数）的长度必须与输出"
"数量相等。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.exp.exp:10 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.exp.exp:13 of
msgid ""
"For other keyword-only arguments, see the :ref:`ufunc docs "
"<ufuncs.kwargs>`."
msgstr "对于其他仅限关键字的参数，请参见 :ref:`ufunc 文档 <ufuncs.kwargs>`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.exp.exp of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.exp.exp:16 of
msgid "**out** -- Output tensor, element-wise exponential of `x`."
msgstr "**out** -- 输出张量，`x` 的逐元素指数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.exp.exp of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.exp.exp:21 of
msgid ":py:obj:`expm1`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.exp.exp:22 of
msgid "Calculate ``exp(x) - 1`` for all elements in the array."
msgstr "计算数组中所有元素的 ``exp(x) - 1``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.exp.exp:24 of
msgid ":py:obj:`exp2`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.exp.exp:25 of
msgid "Calculate ``2**x`` for all elements in the array."
msgstr "计算数组中所有元素的 ``2**x``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.exp.exp:28 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.exp.exp:29 of
msgid ""
"The irrational number ``e`` is also known as Euler's number.  It is "
"approximately 2.718281, and is the base of the natural logarithm, ``ln`` "
"(this means that, if :math:`x = \\ln y = \\log_e y`, then :math:`e^x = "
"y`. For real input, ``exp(x)`` is always positive."
msgstr ""
"无理数 ``e`` 也称为欧拉数。它约等于 2.718281，是自然对数 ``ln`` 的底数（"
"这意味着如果 :math:`x = \\ln y = \\log_e y`，则 :math:`e^x = y`。对于实数"
"输入，``exp(x)`` 始终为正。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.exp.exp:34 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"For complex arguments, ``x = a + ib``, we can write :math:`e^x = e^a "
"e^{ib}`.  The first term, :math:`e^a`, is already known (it is the real "
"argument, described above).  The second term, :math:`e^{ib}`, is "
":math:`\\cos b + i \\sin b`, a function with magnitude 1 and a periodic "
"phase."
msgstr ""
"对于复数参数 ``x = a + ib``，我们可以写成 :math:`e^x = e^a e^{ib}`。"
"第一项 :math:`e^a` 已知（即上述的实数部分）。第二项 :math:`e^{ib}` 是 :"
"math:`\\cos b + i \\sin b`，这是一个幅度为 1 且相位周期的函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.exp.exp:41 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.exp.exp:42 of
msgid ""
"Wikipedia, \"Exponential function\", "
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Exponential_function"
msgstr "Wikipedia, \"指数函数\", http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Exponential_function"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.exp.exp:44 of
msgid ""
"M. Abramovitz and I. A. Stegun, \"Handbook of Mathematical Functions with"
" Formulas, Graphs, and Mathematical Tables,\" Dover, 1964, p. 69, "
"http://www.math.sfu.ca/~cbm/aands/page_69.htm"
msgstr ""
"M. Abramovitz 和 I. A. Stegun, \"数学函数手册：公式、图表和数学表,\" "
"Dover, 1964, 第 69 页, http://www.math.sfu.ca/~cbm/aands/page_69.htm"

